dfischer.utils

Class PerformanceDataRecordFailureInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.PerformanceDataRecordFailureInfo

  • public class PerformanceDataRecordFailureInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains an error situation snapshot at the time when a URL call was failed.

    Hint: all details of the failed URL call itself can examined with PerformanceDataRecord.getFailedUrl().

    See Also:
    PerformanceDataRecord.getFailureInfo(), PerformanceDataRecord.getFailedUrl(dfischer.utils.PerformanceDataRecordFailureInfo)
